@startuml
title Diagrama de Sequencia Geral - Sistema de Moeda Estudantil

hide footbox
autoactivate off
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #374151
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #9CA3AF
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #374151
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F5FF
skinparam sequenceActorBorderColor #374151
skinparam sequenceActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceDatabaseBorderColor #374151
skinparam sequenceDatabaseBackgroundColor #F3E8FF
skinparam sequenceBoundaryBorderColor #374151
skinparam sequenceBoundaryBackgroundColor #ECFEFF
skinparam sequenceControlBorderColor #374151
skinparam sequenceControlBackgroundColor #F0F9FF
skinparam sequenceActivationBorderColor #111827
skinparam sequenceActivationBackgroundColor #CFE3FF
skinparam ParticipantPadding 35
skinparam BoxPadding 12
skinparam maxMessageSize 90

actor Aluno as Aluno
actor Professor as Professor
actor "Empresa Parceira" as Empresa
boundary "Frontend\nNext.js" as Front
control "Controllers\nMicronaut" as Controllers
control "Repositories\nMicronaut Data" as Repos
queue "RabbitMQ\nmoedas.email" as MQ
control "EmailConsumer" as Consumer
control "EmailService" as EmailService
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
collections "Gmail SMTP" as SMTP

group Cadastro de aluno
    Aluno -> Front: Preenche cadastro de aluno
    activate Front

    Front -> Controllers: POST /alunos\nAlunoRequest
    activate Controllers

    Controllers -> Repos: Busca ou cria instituicao
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: SELECT/INSERT instituicao
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Instituicao
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Instituicao associada
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers -> Repos: save(aluno)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: INSERT usuario/aluno
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Aluno salvo
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Aluno
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers --> Front: 201 Created\nAlunoResponse
    deactivate Controllers

    Front --> Aluno: Exibe toast de sucesso
    deactivate Front
end

group Cadastro de empresa parceira
    Empresa -> Front: Preenche cadastro de empresa
    activate Front

    Front -> Controllers: POST /empresas\nEmpresaRequest
    activate Controllers

    Controllers -> Repos: save(empresa)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: INSERT usuario/empresa
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Empresa salva
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Empresa
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers --> Front: 201 Created\nEmpresaResponse
    deactivate Controllers

    Front --> Empresa: Exibe toast de sucesso
    deactivate Front
end

group Cadastro de vantagem
    Empresa -> Front: Acessa painel da empresa
    activate Front

    Front -> Controllers: GET /vantagens/empresa/{empresaId}
    activate Controllers

    Controllers -> Repos: findByEmpresaId(empresaId)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: SELECT vantagens da empresa
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Lista de vantagens
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Vantagens
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers --> Front: VantagemResponse[]
    deactivate Controllers

    Empresa -> Front: Informa nome, descricao, valor e quantidade

    Front -> Controllers: POST /vantagens\nCriarVantagemRequest
    activate Controllers

    Controllers -> Repos: findById(empresaId)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: SELECT empresa
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Empresa
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Empresa
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers -> Repos: save(vantagem)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: INSERT vantagem
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Vantagem salva
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Vantagem
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers --> Front: 201 Created\nVantagemResponse
    deactivate Controllers

    Front --> Empresa: Atualiza painel de vantagens
    deactivate Front
end

group Envio de moedas por merito
    Professor -> Front: Seleciona aluno, valor e motivo
    activate Front

    Front -> Controllers: POST /transacoes\nCriarTransacaoRequest
    activate Controllers

    Controllers -> Repos: findById(professor)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: SELECT professor
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Professor
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Professor
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers -> Repos: findById(aluno)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: SELECT aluno
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Aluno
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Aluno
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers -> Controllers: Valida saldo, curso, instituicao e motivo

    Controllers -> Repos: update(professor)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: UPDATE saldo_corrente
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: OK
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Professor atualizado
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers -> Repos: update(aluno)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: UPDATE saldo_atual
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: OK
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Aluno atualizado
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers -> Repos: save(transacao)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: INSERT transacao
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Transacao salva
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Transacao
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers -> MQ: Publica EnvioMoedasEvent
    activate MQ

    MQ --> Controllers: Mensagem aceita
    deactivate MQ

    Controllers --> Front: 201 Created\nStatusResponse
    deactivate Controllers

    Front --> Professor: Exibe toast de sucesso
    deactivate Front
end

group Notificacao por e-mail do envio de moedas
    MQ -> Consumer: Entrega EnvioMoedasEvent
    activate Consumer

    Consumer -> Repos: Busca transacao, professor e aluno
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: SELECT transacao/professor/aluno
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Dados completos
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Consumer: Dados encontrados
    deactivate Repos

    Consumer -> EmailService: Envia e-mails de confirmacao
    activate EmailService

    EmailService -> SMTP: E-mail para professor
    activate SMTP

    SMTP --> EmailService: OK
    deactivate SMTP

    EmailService -> SMTP: E-mail para aluno
    activate SMTP

    SMTP --> EmailService: OK
    deactivate SMTP

    EmailService --> Consumer: E-mails enviados
    deactivate EmailService

    Consumer --> MQ: ACK da mensagem
    deactivate Consumer

    SMTP --> Professor: Recebe confirmacao do envio
    SMTP --> Aluno: Recebe aviso de moedas
end

group Consulta de perfil, saldo e extrato do aluno
    Aluno -> Front: Acessa perfil do aluno
    activate Front

    Front -> Controllers: GET /alunos/{id}
    activate Controllers

    Controllers -> Repos: findById(alunoId)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: SELECT aluno
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Aluno
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Aluno
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers --> Front: AlunoResponse
    deactivate Controllers

    Front -> Controllers: GET /transacoes/aluno/{id}
    activate Controllers

    Controllers -> Repos: findByDestinatarioId(alunoId)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: SELECT transacoes recebidas
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Extrato
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Lista de transacoes
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers --> Front: ExtratoResponse[]
    deactivate Controllers

    Front -> Controllers: GET /resgates/aluno/{id}
    activate Controllers

    Controllers -> Repos: findByAlunoId(alunoId)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: SELECT resgates
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Resgates
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Lista de resgates
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers --> Front: ResgateResponse[]
    deactivate Controllers

    Front --> Aluno: Exibe saldo, extrato, vantagens e resgates
    deactivate Front
end

group Resgate de vantagem
    Aluno -> Front: Clica em resgatar vantagem
    activate Front

    Front -> Controllers: POST /resgates\n{alunoId, vantagemId}
    activate Controllers

    Controllers -> Repos: Busca aluno e vantagem
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: SELECT aluno e vantagem
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: Aluno e vantagem
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Dados encontrados
    deactivate Repos

    Controllers -> Repos: existsByAlunoIdAndVantagemId(alunoId, vantagemId)
    activate Repos

    Repos -> DB: SELECT EXISTS resgate
    activate DB

    DB --> Repos: true/false
    deactivate DB

    Repos --> Controllers: Resultado
    deactivate Repos

    alt Resgate invalido
        Controllers --> Front: 400 Bad Request\n{erro}
        Front --> Aluno: Exibe toast de erro
    else Resgate valido
        Controllers -> Controllers: Valida saldo e estoque

        Controllers -> Repos: update(aluno)
        activate Repos

        Repos -> DB: UPDATE saldo_atual
        activate DB

        DB --> Repos: OK
        deactivate DB

        Repos --> Controllers: Aluno atualizado
        deactivate Repos

        Controllers -> Repos: update(vantagem)
        activate Repos

        Repos -> DB: UPDATE quantidade_disponivel
        activate DB

        DB --> Repos: OK
        deactivate DB

        Repos --> Controllers: Vantagem atualizada
        deactivate Repos

        Controllers -> Repos: save(resgate)
        activate Repos

        Repos -> DB: INSERT resgate_vantagem
        activate DB

        DB --> Repos: Resgate salvo
        deactivate DB

        Repos --> Controllers: Resgate
        deactivate Repos

        Controllers --> Front: 201 Created\nResgateResponse
        Front -> Front: Recarrega dados do aluno
        Front --> Aluno: Exibe toast de sucesso
    end

    deactivate Controllers
    deactivate Front
end

@enduml